org.conqat.lib.commons.uniformpath

Class UniformPathCompatibilityUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.conqat.lib.commons.uniformpath.UniformPathCompatibilityUtil

  • public class UniformPathCompatibilityUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility methods to aid the migration from string-typed uniform paths to type-safe UniformPaths. Can be removed when/if string-typed uniform paths are no longer relevant.
